				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Now how did pets fall so far behind...Original EQ all was hunky dory, Kunark was sweet but they broke our Fire pets, Velious we got Visual Candy pets, Luclin no pet upgrades at all and junk AAs, PoP woot we can function in Upper Luclin now, LoY nadda...LDoN nadda...GoD MS4 (ya know that pet 90% of the mages dont have)
<br />
OoW wow were effective in PoP now...wait PoP isn't this expansion...awwww hell.....
<br />

<br />
I propsed we should get 3 pet upgrades (the 1st one was almost identical to what we got, yet but no additional pets were gained. ) 
<br />

<br />
Sice the begining Mages and Necro's pets were the nasty monsters, but as a Part of our class that can only be upgraded when the level cap goes up (other than the MS line or overhauling all pets), we have fallen behind. NO melee was penelized in DPS by gaining levels...no caster was penelized in DPS by gaining levels...except 1..US. Now Pet foci scale...come on what the hell are they thinking. Now our pets get weaker as we go up in level as well...soon we will ding some unknow level and will nuke for 1/5th of a wizard and have a pet that dies when a mob looks at it from 5 expansions ago.
<br />

<br />
-Mages are a silk class...yet we are surpassing our pets in HPs
<br />
-Mages are a DPS class...yet Priests are neck and neck in nukes
<br />
-Mages are the Pet Class...yet the "supeiror" pets are really just marginaly better than other pet classes
<br />
-Mages sacrifice all defences for our monster pets...yet they can not defend us
<br />
-Mages rely on our pets...yet our 51+ fire pets have been non viable since Kunark
<br />

<br />
To Fix this problem from continuing we need 
<br />
pet HP/Surivability doubled
<br />
Nukes increased an additional 25%
<br />
Pet DPS incrased another 50-75%
<br />
--OR--
<br />
Change the levels of our pets to 66 Air, 67 Water, 68 Earth and 69 MS 5 (lose the broke fire pets since they refuse to fix them)
<br />

<br />
I would also like to Propose a Ancient:Summon Elemental Vortex (name unimportant) that is a remake of our Epic Pet, hitting in the range of 140's, procing as did our 1st epic but for 200s (instead of 143), level 66 unfocused, 8000 hps, 100pt DS, and a casted stun for 2 sec doing 300 every 6 seconds. Why so many hp/dam/etc... because we will not get a new pet increase in power for a minimum of several expansions. This will put us ahead in pet power. Why a remake of our Epic, what other version of our pet was Viable for high end content over 2 expansions in a row, why to this day several still use the epic over air and it still was our highest DPS pet of all the PoP and GoD pets.
<br />
 
<br />
But wont the BST and Necro's bitch...yes BUT i also would like to see them receive an Ancient Pet as well but following along the lines of their classes. All 3 of us rely on our pets some less than others, but we all relly on them to some extent. 
<br />

<br />
Most will think theses changes would be to late but they changed several spells months and years after they 1st came out for various reasons. Changing the level of 1 pet (earth) twinking the MS4 fr a lv 69 MS5 version will be fairely easy as well, and reworking the Epic pet for a NEW Ancient spell. All fairely easy to do as they have bases to work from.<br />_________________<br />Syanu
