Yes a pet hitting in the base 140 range is exactly what the OOW pets should be, though I disagree with our nukes being increased 25% as well.  If pets scaled properly each expansion (compared to mobs and compared to other caster DPS) we wouldn't need further enhanced nukes.
<br />

