If u read higher up you will see what i stated, that is that my pet was able to tank tipt, vxed, wall of slaugther, hard ldon, kod taz, elemental planes etc. no i didnt have 2 clerics spam healing him or stuff, yes i did have mobs slowed what do you xpect, have you ever tried tipt ? then you know if you use complete heal on a elemental geared tank hes most likly to die ? so you use sup  heal, and yes cleric was using sup heal on my pet (on the mobs who was lvl 66).
<br />
I also stated i was using WoX pet not MS4 or the omens pet.
<br />

<br />
If you check my magelo you will see i  have no avoidance or shielding, such things come first with time/middle+ GoD and i BELIEVE ! that even with those things mage pets are better tanks that the mage.
<br />
Since the pet patch this spring (6 months ago or so) mage pets are actually viable tanks if you want them to<br />_________________<br />Master of the elements !
